item.title: Fire it Up - B-w3ll
item.dc:creator: Chaff
item.description:
It’s really good and full of flavour and I have no complaints at all except for the intro and end.

The intro felt drawn out a bit before the sound modifications kicked in. If they played a bit sooner it would be a much better start. Adding an ambience to it in the start also is very beneficial.

The end was also great, with the orchestral instruments blending in with the electronics, but the ending felt abrupt. I didn’t expect for the song to end there.

Other than that, it’s amazing and flows through perfectly.
